humanMachineDialogue.author: Memory Reasoning
humanMachineDialogue.text: According to the report, sentinel lymph node #1, sentinel lymph node #2, and non-sentinel lymph node from the left axilla are all negative for metastases (0/1). This indicates that there are no metastatic carcinomas in the sentinel lymph nodes and regional lymph nodes (New Rule 10 and New Rule 11). Therefore, the N stage is N0.
